# Claude Code: reference tool clones used locally to source agent/skill
# templates. Each of these is its own git checkout (has its own .git/), so
# committing them would embed broken nested repos and megabytes of content
# unrelated to VitaHub. The curated, VitaHub-specific agents/skills we
# actually use live in .claude/agents/ and .claude/skills/, which ARE
# tracked — only these raw source clones are ignored.
.claude/agents-pro/
.claude/caveman/
.claude/skills-345/
